data.description: BACK ON THE MARKET - NEW ROOF & HOT WATER HEATER WILL BE ADDED BEFORE CLOSING! Downtown DeLand beauty with spectacular PRIVATE OUTDOOR LIVING! Looking for that perfect downtown location in a highly sought after community, close to shopping, good food, entertainment and local events? Here is a SOLID well built home with quality craftsmanship and loads of UPDATES! This 3 bedroom 2 bath home with IN-LAW SUITE includes its own private entrance with additional bathroom as well as poolside benefits. The 3 main house bedrooms come with oversized cedar lined closets as well as upgraded waterproof commercial grade luxury vinyl flooring. You will find Anderson windows with complimenting birch trim running throughout the home & completely UPDATED BATHROOMS.    The spacious GOURMET KITCHEN is any Chef's DREAM! Beautiful maple cabinets with an abundance of work space and endless storage are just the beginning. It features a generous island, 2 refrigerators, gas range with convection oven, a second built-in oven, double basin hammered copper sink, slate & copper backsplash, copper range hood, handsome granite counters, and reverse osmosis water system. All this overlooking your SPARKLING SPORTS STYLE SALT WATER POOL with WATERFALL, spacious poolside CABANA, wood burning stone FIREPLACE (with gas starter hookup option), a natural gas grill with outdoor seating, and a gas connection for outdoor space heater to complete this PERFECTLY PRIVATE ENTERTAINMENT OASIS. There is space to expand the already present garden featuring lime, lemon, mandarin oranges, ruby red grapefruit, navel oranges, pomegranate, avocado trees as well as an abundance of herbs. The drought tolerant & low maintenance landscaping includes slate walkways that guide you around the entire property, circular driveway, and fully enclosed brick & chain link fence. Do not miss this DOWNTOWN GEM! Minutes from award winning Downtown DeLand and Stetson University.
